      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws and 5.5 mm rods were tested across two independent laboratories (n=6 and n=5). All samples were drawn from the same production lot and are traceable by serial number. Sample size provides adequate statistical power for the acceptance criterion evaluation."
