    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the high relevance of the validation activity to the COU, the multi-laboratory experimental dataset, and the conservative acceptance bounds applied to all QoIs. The overall credibility profile supports an Accepted determination at Medium assurance level for the stated context of use.",
